io.nats.stan

Class ConnectionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nats.stan.ConnectionFactory

  • public class ConnectionFactory
extends Object
    A ConnectionFactory object encapsulates a set of connection configuration options. A client uses it to create a connection to the STAN streaming data system.
